sentence: Former President Donald Trump speaks at a rally at the Canyon Moon Ranch festival grounds in Florence, Ariz. | Mario Tama/Getty Images By Meridith McGraw 02/17/2022 04:17 PM EST Former President Donald Trump and his allies have been privately lobbying Wyoming lawmakers to change the state's election laws as part of an effort to unseat Rep. title: Trump moves to close off Liz Cheney's political escape hatch
